# 6. Database Schema Direction

The database should be SQLite and local-first.

Principle:

```text
Raw runs are the source of truth.
Aggregates are derived.
```

Recommended SQLite settings:

```sql
PRAGMA foreign_keys = ON;
PRAGMA journal_mode = WAL;
PRAGMA synchronous = NORMAL;
```

Use migrations and indexes.

