# 13. Feedback / Summary Modes

Feedback modes:

```text
Off
Minimal
Normal
Detailed
Custom
```

## Off

No automatic summaries shown. The app still logs runs and updates stats.

## Minimal

Only important summaries:

- end of session
- weekly report
- major PB/milestone alerts if enabled

## Normal

Default:

- optional scenario block summaries
- end-of-session summary
- daily summary
- weekly report

## Detailed

For users who want more feedback:

- scenario summaries
- category summaries
- session summaries
- daily summaries
- weekly reports
- monthly reviews
- more coach notes

## Custom

User toggles each type individually:

- Scenario block summary
- Category summary
- Session summary
- Daily summary
- Weekly coach report
- Monthly review
- PB popup
- Coach recommendation popup
- Goal alert
- Import issue alert

## Quiet mode while training

When enabled:

- no popups during active training
- summaries wait until session ends
- critical import errors can still be shown quietly
- PBs can be stored silently

