# 19. Testing Strategy

Importer and database tests matter more than UI polish.

## Highest priority tests

### Import parser tests

- extracts scenario name
- extracts score
- extracts timestamp
- handles missing optional fields
- preserves unknown safe fields
- fails clearly on invalid format

### Duplicate detection tests

- same source_run_id = exact duplicate
- same scenario/score/timestamp = probable duplicate
- same score but different timestamp = not duplicate or possible duplicate
- re-import same file does not double-count runs

### Scenario matching tests

- exact alias matches
- normalized name matches
- unknown scenario becomes review item
- similar but not identical names are not blindly merged

### Database tests

- migrations apply
- foreign keys work
- raw run inserted correctly
- import batch links to runs
- calculated stats derive from raw_runs

### Analytics tests

- PB calculation
- latest score
- last-5 average
- last-10 average
- trend calculation
- category summary

### Session summary tests

- runs close in time are grouped
- long gap creates new session
- PB count in session
- basic coach note generated from known pattern

